cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.SY, cs.IT, cs.MA. 

The paper deals with the analysis of a distributed optimization algorithm, which is a common topic in machine learning and control systems, hence cs.LG and cs.SY are likely categories. The algorithm is based on diffusion strategies, which are often used in networked systems, making cs.NE another likely category. The paper also involves mathematical analysis of the algorithm, which could fall under cs.IT and cs.MA.
